name: Artículos mas Comprados
query:
SELECT `tabPurchase Order Item`.`item_code` AS `item_code`, sum(`tabPurchase Order Item`.`qty`) AS `sum`
FROM `tabPurchase Order Item`
WHERE (`tabPurchase Order Item`.`docstatus` = 1)
GROUP BY `tabPurchase Order Item`.`item_code`
ORDER BY `sum` DESC, `tabPurchase Order Item`.`item_code` ASC
LIMIT 10
